&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>MVC 디자인 패턴&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Servlet과 DispatcherServlet의 역할&lt;/li>
&lt;li>View Resolver, HttpMessageConverter 작동 원리&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
